              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The reaction Li-7(gamma,p+t)H-3 was searched using the",
                "thick-layer photoplates loaded with the Li-7 isotope,",
                "in the gamma-quanta energy range 23-27 MeV. The energy",
                "dependence of the cross section is obtained. The",
                "integral reaction  cross section in the mentioned",
                "energy region is found to be 1.0(0.1) MeV*mb."
